gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Suns 110, Rockets 105
gameRecap.excerpt: The Suns defeated the Rockets, 110-105. Devin Booker recorded 35 points, seven rebounds, and three assists for the Suns, with Kevin Durant adding 24 points, seven rebounds, and six assists in the victory. Jalen Green tallied 34 points, five rebounds, and three steals for the Rockets in the losing effort. The Suns improve to 35-24, while the Rockets fall to 25-34.
